OL,6,     FOfficers make a massive seizure of
OL,7,     Fmeth hidden inside fruit crates, a
OL,8,     Fformer teacher is taken surprise
OL,9,     Fby a warrant for her arrest, and a
OL,10,     FSyrian man begs for help.
OL,11,G0920 Border Force America's Gatekeepers
